      <title>拉脱维亚联盟将央行行长选举推迟至明年一月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/latvian-coalition-delays-central-bank-governor-choice-until-jan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉脱维亚总理埃维卡·西利纳 (Evika Silina) 在社交媒体上表示，拉脱维亚执政党在周四举行的投票之前意外撤回了下一任央行行长的提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/latvian-coalition-delays-central-bank-governor-choice-until-jan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 18:20:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多的政治危机撕毁了与特朗普的贸易战策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/trudeau-s-political-crisis-rips-up-playbook-for-trade-fight-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰决定辞去加拿大财政部长一职，这不仅仅是一场震动加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政治地震，还将改变美国、加拿大和墨西哥之间即将到来的贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/trudeau-s-political-crisis-rips-up-playbook-for-trade-fight-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 17:51:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克涉嫌与俄罗斯接触令美国空军司令肯德尔担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/musk-s-alleged-russia-contacts-worry-us-air-force-chief-kendall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国空军部长弗兰克·肯德尔 (Frank Kendall) 告诉民主党参议员，他和民主党参议员一样对伊隆·马斯克与俄罗斯领导人接触一事感到担忧，但他补充说，五角大楼在太空计划方面有足够的竞争力，可以防止过度依赖这位亿万富翁的 SpaceX。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/musk-s-alleged-russia-contacts-worry-us-air-force-chief-kendall</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 17:43:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>僵局加剧 哥伦比亚愿意为马杜罗对手提供保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/colombia-offers-to-safeguard-foes-of-venezuela-s-maduro-as-standoff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚已提出接管阿根廷驻加拉加斯大使馆，自三月份以来，反对派领导人玛丽亚·科里纳·马查多的六名助手一直躲藏在该大使馆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/colombia-offers-to-safeguard-foes-of-venezuela-s-maduro-as-standoff-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 17:40:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚预算紧缩加剧 暂停住房补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/colombia-suspends-housing-subsidies-in-worsening-budget-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府财政账户问题蔓延至社会项目，哥伦比亚将暂停旨在帮助弱势家庭的住房补贴申请。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/colombia-suspends-housing-subsidies-in-worsening-budget-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 16:34:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西财政部长称雷亚尔可能遭受“投机攻击”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/brazil-finance-chief-says-real-may-be-under-speculative-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长费尔南多·阿达德表示，在财政担忧加剧引发的抛售中，巴西雷亚尔可能面临“投机性攻击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/brazil-finance-chief-says-real-may-be-under-speculative-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 16:27:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院将审理 TikTok 对美国即将实施的禁令的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/supreme-court-will-hear-tiktok-challenge-to-us-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，将审理 TikTok 对一项法律的质疑，该法律规定如果 TikTok 不被其中国母公司出售，该公司将禁止该社交媒体应用，并将以异常快速的方式安排在 1 月 10 日进行辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/supreme-court-will-hear-tiktok-challenge-to-us-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 16:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关键顾问马斯克反对年底拨款法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/us-government-funding-fight-previews-house-republican-turbulence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克加大了对众议院议长迈克·约翰逊达成的临时政府拨款协议的公开批评，加大了政府关门的可能性，并宣称任何支持该法案的议员都应在两年内被投票罢免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/us-government-funding-fight-previews-house-republican-turbulence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:49:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯兰叛军取得胜利后叙利亚下一步将何去何从？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/after-victory-of-hts-islamist-rebels-in-syria-what-s-next-for-the-country-m4rbr6x9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月初，一群伊斯兰叛乱分子突然攻入首都大马士革，推翻了叙利亚总统巴沙尔·阿萨德的专制政权。该组织名为“解放沙姆组织”，由激进的基地组织发展而来，已宣布成立临时政府来管理其控制的地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/after-victory-of-hts-islamist-rebels-in-syria-what-s-next-for-the-country-m4rbr6x9</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:01:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
